verbose_text: The following imaging and clinical findings were compared between baseline (time 0) and 12-month follow-up : menstrual bleeding pattern, dysmenorrhea, visual analog scale (VAS) pain score, uterine volume, serum cancer antigen 125 (CA125) levels, hemoglobin, follicle stimulating hormone (FSH) levels, luteinizing hormone levels, serum estradiol levels, and any treatment side effects.
